hints.message:
SyntaxError: Missing semicolon at end of statement.
→ Every JavaScript statement ends with ;
→ Try: console.log("hello");

ReferenceError: JavaScript is case-sensitive!
→ "console" must be all lowercase.
→ Try: console.log("hello");

ArgumentError: Missing string argument.
→ Specify a target in quotes.
→ Example: scan("office");

ArgumentError: Missing string argument.
→ Specify a target in quotes.
→ Example: inspect("desk");

SyntaxError: Use dot notation to call a method on an object.
→ Pattern: object.method("argument");
→ Example: desk.read("open_book");

SyntaxError: Use dot notation to call a method on an object.
→ Pattern: object.method("argument");
→ Example: desk.read("clipboard");

ArgumentError: Missing string argument.
→ Specify a target in quotes.
→ Example: inspect("plant");

ArgumentError: That is not a valid key.
→ Use the item in your inventory.
→ Try: drawers.unlock("key");
